towers
the Towers have a drawbridge at their entrance.  To lower the drawbridge, push the button marked AHN first, then the one marked ORT.  There are seven in total.
drawbridge
the drawbridge has four buttons to push.  The first one must be AHN, and the second one must be ORT.  You must push the buttons seven times.
buttons
you must push the button marked AHN first, and the button marked ORT second.  There are seven total.

